1
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Did I tell you? If anyone knows this, you will be in trouble.

2
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:23,000
Madam, please. Mr. Tian will die.

3
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:25,000
What does homosexual mean?

4
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:30,000
It refers to a man who loves another man.

5
00:00:30,400 --> 00:00:33,000
Or we call them gay.

6
00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:37,000
A person of your kind can get married and have heirs.

7
00:00:37,500 --> 00:00:39,000
A homosexual like me can have an heir.

8
00:00:39,700 --> 00:00:41,000
But I don't want to, Mother.

9
00:00:41,700 --> 00:00:44,000
Mr. Tian is homosexual. He's gay.

10
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:46,000
Aren't you going to tell Tian's secret? Tell me then.

11
00:00:46,700 --> 00:00:49,000
If you don't have enough money, I won't dare to risk.

12
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:52,000
They will solve the problem for us.

13
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Do we have to do this?

14
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:57,000
We have no other choice, Madam.

15
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,000
Dong.

16
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,000
Dong.

17
00:01:03,700 --> 00:01:05,000
Madam Chan.

18
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:07,000
Dong's voice.

19
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:09,000
I didn't see anyone,

20
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:11,000
and I didn't hear anyone either.

21
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:16,000
It is called beetle orchid.

22
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:20,000
It is a poisonous mushroom that grows in the insects.

23
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:24,000
It usually doesn't grow in human.

24
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:30,000
But I ground it and mixed it with special ingredients for you.

25
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:47,000
Its poison would make you numb, unable to move.

26
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:51,000
If you breathes in or consumed it,

27
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:55,000
