28
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:58,000
Sucking your blood and flesh as its food.

29
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,000
After that,

30
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:04,000
the poisonous mushrooms will grow all over the body

31
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:08,000
and torture you to death.

32
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,000
But don't worry.

33
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,000
You won't suffer that much.

34
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,000
Jia.

35
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:22,000
If you aren't comfortable to stay here, you can go back. I'll see you later.

36
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:32,000
Be careful.

37
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:22,000
Guanyin, Goddess of Mercy.

38
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,000
I've made a mistake,

39
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,000
but I need to do it

40
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,000
for my son.

41
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,000
Done, Madam.

42
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,000
Li.

43
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,000
Where is she?

44
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:58,000
Mr. Song, something bad happened.

45
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,000
What happened?

46
00:07:59,100 --> 00:08:00,000
Dong went missing.

47
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:06,000
Where will he be? Are you searching through the place?

48
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,000
Have you found him?

49
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:12,000
He can't go missing so easily.

50
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,000
Father.

51
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,000
How is it?

52
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,100
I didn't see him.

53
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,000
I think if Dong didn't run away,

54
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:27,000
He must have been drunk at the bar like he usually does.

55
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,000
I don't think so.

56
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:37,000
If you want to know where Dong is, ask Madam Li.

57
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,000
What are you talking about?

58
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,000
Right.

59
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:49,000
Aunt Chan talked like Mother knows about Dong's disappearance.

60
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:52,000
The other day, Dong came to me,

61
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:54,000
saying he got something important to talk about.

62
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:57,000
But Madam Li intervened and took him away.

63
00:09:58,000 --> 00:10:01,000
Since then, when I asked him anything,

64
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,000
