65
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:06,000
Last night I looked for him at his room.

66
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,000
But he's gone already.

67
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:11,000
I don't know what he's like now.

68
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,000
And most importantly,

69
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:18,000
the incident happened after Dong had a fight with Tian.

70
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:25,000
His disappearance must have something to do with it.

71
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,000
How is it relevant?

72
00:10:27,300 --> 00:10:31,000
It is. Madam Li killed Dong to protect Tian.

73
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:40,000
What do you mean?

74
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:41,000
It's about… / Shut up.

75
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:45,000
I speak the truth, sir. It is …

76
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:46,000
I told you to shut up.

77
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,000
In front of so many people, how could you talk like this?

78
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,000
You guys.

79
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,000
Go talk to me in the hall.

80
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,000
Chan.

81
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:28,000
You must be careful with your words when you were in front of many workers.

82
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:32,000
You said that Dong disappeared last night?

83
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:38,000
Yes. Nuan and I went looking for him all night and couldn't find him.

84
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:42,000
I thought it might Madam who did this.

85
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:47,000
You can't accuse me without evidence like this.

86
00:11:47,300 --> 00:11:50,000
Despite no evidence, it is a fact.

87
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:54,000
The other day, Dong was going to tell me a secret about Tian.

88
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:59,000
This secret that can put him out of the family leadership position.

89
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:03,000
Then later, Dong harassed and attacked a worker.

90
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:06,000
He also disrespected Tian.

91
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:10,000
But she gave in to Dong.

92
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:13,000
It was clear that

93
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:16,000
this must definitely be about Tian's secret.

94
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,000
Tian's secret?

95
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,000
What is this about?

96
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:24,000
Does Tian have a secret?

97
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,000
I doubt that.

98
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,000
What secret?

99
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,000
Dong must have seen that Chan was trying to push Yang

100
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:36,000
to become the clan leader instead of Tian.

101
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:40,000
So he made up a story to trick Chan for money.

102
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,000
Consider it carefully, sir.

103
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:46,000
When Dong said that he knew the secret,

104
00:12:46,700 --> 00:12:48,000
he suddenly disappeared.

105
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:53,000
I couldn't help thinking that he has been killed already.

106
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,000
Madam.

107
00:12:57,000 --> 00:13:01,000
You'd better confess what you did to Dong last night.

108
00:13:01,700 --> 00:13:03,000
Stop accusing Madam Li, please.

109
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:08,000
Mr. Song is a wise and rational man. He won't listen to your nonsense.

110
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,000
Right.

111
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,000
I'm rational.

112
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:19,000
Li.

113
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,000
Where have you been last night?

114
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,000
I woke up in the middle of the night,

115
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,000
but I didn't see you there.

116
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:38,000
I had a bad dream, so I went to the Buddhist altar.

117
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,000
You never pray at the Buddhist altar.

118
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:46,000
Once a man went missing, you immediately did it.

119
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,000
Mr. Song.

120
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:51,000
Think carefully who benefits from this.

121
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:54,000
One missing worker.

122
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:59,000
But you make a fuss and blame Madam Li despite the lack of evidence.

123
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,000
Maybe it's you

124
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:05,000
