265
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:01,000
Aunt Jia.

266
00:27:01,700 --> 00:27:03,000
Where did you guys put Dong's body?

267
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:07,000
I heard the workers saying they would take the body to the temple.

268
00:27:07,300 --> 00:27:08,000
But I don't know what temple.

269
00:27:09,000 --> 00:27:12,000
Why do you ask about Dong's body all of a sudden?

270
00:27:12,700 --> 00:27:15,000
What that has to do with you?

271
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:19,000
I'm just wondering. Usually, you don't care about him.

272
00:27:19,500 --> 00:27:22,000
But when he died, you asked about him.

273
00:27:23,000 --> 00:27:25,000
Ew, you talking about body and body again.

