00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:28,000
I can't eat anything.

275
00:27:28,700 --> 00:27:31,000
I can still imagine Dong's bloated body.

276
00:27:32,000 --> 00:27:35,000
Mud, at first I forgot about it already.

277
00:27:35,700 --> 00:27:37,000
When you said that, I could see it too.

278
00:27:39,000 --> 00:27:41,000
Madam Li asked me to take care of the workers.

279
00:27:41,600 --> 00:27:43,000
Even if he was a bad guy,

280
00:27:43,500 --> 00:27:47,000
But we have take care of his funeral ceremony.

281
00:27:47,600 --> 00:27:49,000
Did he have any relatives?

282
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:53,000
He didn't have any relatives.

283
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:56,000
We've already carried his body to the temple.

284
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:59,000
Is that so?

285
00:28:00,000 --> 00:28:02,000
And what temple did you take Dong's body to?

286
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:09,000
The workers said that Dong's body was taken to a Thai temple near the end of the market.

287
00:28:09,700 --> 00:28:12,000
I think I should follow to destroy the body.

288
00:28:12,500 --> 00:28:16,000
Otherwise there will be evidence that he died unnaturally.

289
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,000
Please take care of it, Jia.

290
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:33,000
It is called beetle orchid.

291
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:36,000
It is a poisonous mushroom that grows in the insects.

292
00:28:37,000 --> 00:28:40,000
If you breathes in or consumed it,

293
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:43,000
it will accelerate its growth in your body.

294
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:46,000
Sucking your blood and flesh as its food.

295
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,000
After that,

296
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:52,000
the poisonous mushrooms will grow all over the body

297
00:29:09,700 --> 00:29:12,000
You don't think that Dong drowned?

298
00:29:12,300 --> 00:29:14,000
So you come to inspect the boat again.

299
00:29:14,500 --> 00:29:17,000
I just wanted to make sure that no one really attacked Dong.

300
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:22,000
Since he died in our home like this.

301
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:25,000
The more I examined it, the more I found it strange.

302
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:29,000
But the crack is …

303
00:29:31,000 --> 00:29:33,000
It got sharp edges like that when someone punched it.

304
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:37,000
Bua.

305
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:40,000
Didn't you see anything?

306
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:45,000
Mr. Yang.

307
00:29:46,000 --> 00:29:49,000
When I found a dead body, there was nothing strange about it.

308
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:52,000
But the night before the body was found,

309
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:57,000
I looked out of my house and saw something.

310
00:29:57,400 --> 00:29:59,000
A silhouette of someone.

311
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:05,000
She looks like …

312
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:08,000
Madam Li.

313
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:12,000
That night, Madam Li came out in the middle of the night too?

314
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:18,000
I think it probably was. But Mr. Yang,

315
00:30:19,000 --> 00:30:23,000
she wasn't the only one who came out that night.

316
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:29,000
I was out there and met Madam Chan and Nuan as well.

317
00:30:29,600 --> 00:30:32,000
I told you that I went out to find Dong

318
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:35,000
because I had something to talk to him.

319
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:37,000
Are you manipulating my son?

320
00:30:37,700 --> 00:30:38,200
Bua didn't do anything, Mom.

321
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:40,000
Then why are you talking about it?

322
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:47,000
Or do you suspect about Dong's death as well?

323
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:50,000
Who is suspicious? Is it Madam Li?

324
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:51,000
Me too.

325
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:55,000
If we work together, we can find a way to expose her.

326
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:03,000
Bua.

327
00:31:07,000 --> 00:31:09,000
Mr. Song and Madam Li want to see you.

328
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:28,000
Bua is here.

329
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:29,000
Yes, Madam.

330
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:31,000
Sit down.

331
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:38,000
What would you like me to do, Sir, Madam?

332
00:31:49,000 --> 00:31:53,000
Tian, come in, come in. Bua is here now.

333
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:10,000
What is this, Madam, Sir?

334
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:14,000
Li discussed with me.

335
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:17,000
She wants to let you

336
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:20,000
become Tian's adoptive mother.

337
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:24,000
Madam.

338
00:32:24,600 --> 00:32:28,000
I see that you love Tian like your real child

339
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:30,000
and always watch over him.

340
00:32:30,800 --> 00:32:33,000
So today I want to make it formal.

341
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:39,000
Everyone will know that you are Tian's second mother.

342
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:44,000
But I don't want to…

343
00:32:44,200 --> 00:32:45,000
Aunt Bua.

344
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:48,000
You don't want to be my mother?

345
00:32:49,000 --> 00:32:50,000
Tian.

346
00:32:50,200 --> 00:32:51,000
Please.

347
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:54,000
Tian has been kneeling down for a while now. His kneels hurt.

348
00:32:58,000 --> 00:33:01,000
Hurry, Tian. Give her the tea.

349
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:14,000
Tian.

350
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:32,000
Madam Li must have a plan.

351
00:33:45,000 --> 00:33:47,000
Bua, eat more.

352
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:49,000
Thank you, Madam.

353
00:33:49,700 --> 00:33:51,000
Have some vegetables, Bua.

354
00:33:51,300 --> 00:33:54,000
Thanks.
Here yours, sir.

355
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:58,000
Today we're having dinner together.

356
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:01,000
I really have good appetite.

357
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:05,000
Li, thank you

358
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:07,000
for being generous to Bua.

359
00:34:07,600 --> 00:34:10,000
I'm the one who has to thank her

360
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:13,000
for taking care of Tian for more than ten years.

361
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:18,000
Today, I let Tian be your son as well.

362
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:24,000
Hope you love, care for and protect Tian

363
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:28,000
just like a mother should do for her child.

364
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:30,000
Yes, Madam.

365
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:33,000
So that's why!

366
00:34:33,699 --> 00:34:34,999
You want Bua to protect Tian.

367
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:38,000
What did he do?

368
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:41,000
Why does he need two mothers to protect him?

369
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:44,000
Mom.

370
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:48,000
Chan.

371
00:34:48,699 --> 00:34:51,999
Is it very painful for you to see Li and Bua getting along well?

372
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:57,000
Instead of being happy that our family lives peacefully,

373
00:34:58,000 --> 00:35:00,000
you keep nitpicking.

374
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:02,000
When I say something,

375
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:06,000
it turns out that I'm slandering others, right?

376
00:35:06,500 --> 00:35:07,000
You always cause trouble.

377
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:10,000
You'd better take your time to take care of Yang.

378
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:12,000
So he won't be ridiculous like this.

379
00:35:13,000 --> 00:35:14,000
Father, please calm down.

380
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:17,000
Yang was not that ridiculous at all.

381
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:18,000
Don't pretend to help him!

382
00:35:18,200 --> 00:35:19,000
Chan.

383
00:35:44,500 --> 00:35:45,500
Is Yang my child alone?

384
00:35:46,500 --> 00:35:48,500
Isn't he your son as well?

385
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:52,500
Why is it my fault to raise the kid alone?

386
00:35:53,500 --> 00:35:58,500
Why don't you think that it's because you don't love your sons equally?

387
00:35:59,500 --> 00:36:01,500
Mom, that's okay.

388
00:36:02,000 --> 00:36:03,500
Don't say anything that is not auspicious.

389
00:36:04,500 --> 00:36:06,500
There are good food here. Let's eat.

390
00:36:06,700 --> 00:36:08,500
Because of you. You are like this.

391
00:36:09,500 --> 00:36:10,500
Not serious about anything.

392
00:36:12,500 --> 00:36:13,500
Listen carefully.

393
00:36:14,500 --> 00:36:16,500
If I didn't think Yang is my son,

394
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:19,500
I would have drove you and him out earlier.

395
00:36:20,500 --> 00:36:21,500
Please stop, Sir.

396
00:36:35,500 --> 00:36:38,500
Right, I slander other people.

397
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:40,500
And my son is ridiculous.

398
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:43,500
There's nothing good about the two of us at all, right?

399
00:36:49,500 --> 00:36:50,500
Mom.

400
00:36:53,500 --> 00:36:54,500
Mom.

401
00:36:55,500 --> 00:36:56,500
Chan.

402
00:36:58,500 --> 00:37:01,500
Sir, don't be mad at this nonsense.

403
00:37:03,500 --> 00:37:04,500
Come on.

404
00:37:05,500 --> 00:37:06,500
Let's eat.

405
00:37:16,500 --> 00:37:17,500
Please excuse me.

406
00:38:18,500 --> 00:38:19,500
You see it now?

407
00:38:21,500 --> 00:38:24,500
He's never care about us.

408
00:38:26,500 --> 00:38:29,500
No matter what I say or do,

409
00:38:30,500 --> 00:38:33,500
It is annoying in his eyes.

410
00:38:37,500 --> 00:38:39,500
I'm the daughter of a lord.

411
00:38:41,500 --> 00:38:46,500
But your father listens to that low-class opera lead actress like Li rather than me.

412
00:38:56,500 --> 00:38:57,500
It's okay.

413
00:38:58,500 --> 00:38:59,500
It's alright.

414
00:39:00,500 --> 00:39:01,500
In the past, I used to think

415
00:39:03,500 --> 00:39:07,500
that if you behave well and do your job,

416
00:39:08,500 --> 00:39:12,500
your father probably appreciates the two of us more.

417
00:39:13,500 --> 00:39:16,500
But I know now. No matter how good we are,

418
00:39:17,500 --> 00:39:18,500
we'll just stay in the same place.

419
00:39:19,500 --> 00:39:20,500
You know why?

420
00:39:21,500 --> 00:39:23,500
Because I'm just the second wife.

421
00:39:25,500 --> 00:39:28,500
I always have to be under the first wife.

422
00:39:29,200 --> 00:39:31,500
No one respects and listens to me.

423
00:39:36,500 --> 00:39:37,500
Mom, listen to me.

424
00:39:39,500 --> 00:39:41,500
No matter what Father or whoever says,

425
00:39:42,500 --> 00:39:43,500
but for me,

426
00:39:45,500 --> 00:39:49,500
you are the most valuable. No need to be praised by anyone.

427
00:39:52,500 --> 00:39:53,500
If it were only me,

428
00:39:54,500 --> 00:39:55,500
I got used to it.

429
00:39:57,500 --> 00:40:02,500
But I couldn't bear to see you as his subordinate for the rest of your life.

430
00:40:03,500 --> 00:40:05,500
So I struggle to do everything for you.

431
00:40:07,500 --> 00:40:09,500
When I know that Tian has a big secret

432
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:13,500
to the extent that Madam Li struggled to cover it up, I can't let go of this.

433
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:15,500
But I don't want you to interfere.

434
00:40:16,500 --> 00:40:18,300
Do you know it's dangerous?

435
00:40:18,500 --> 00:40:21,500
Taking a risk it better than living under the wicked.

436
00:40:23,500 --> 00:40:26,500
I will prove that she killed people to hide a secret for Tian.

437
00:40:29,500 --> 00:40:32,500
Evil people shouldn't live a good life.

438
00:40:52,500 --> 00:40:53,500
Noi.

439
00:40:54,500 --> 00:40:57,500
The newspaper announced that a new mall has opened. There's a lot of stuff there.

440
00:40:58,500 --> 00:41:01,500
Do you think they will accept more workers?

441
00:41:02,200 --> 00:41:03,500
Oh my lady.

442
00:41:03,900 --> 00:41:06,500
Do you really have to find jobs?

443
00:41:07,500 --> 00:41:09,500
I've studied a lot. I should go out and earn money.

444
00:41:11,500 --> 00:41:12,500
Or …

445
00:41:13,500 --> 00:41:16,500
Should I work at this newspaper?

446
00:41:17,500 --> 00:41:19,500
I'm an educated woman. I won't starve to death.

447
00:41:19,800 --> 00:41:22,500
Come, come, come in

448
00:41:31,500 --> 00:41:33,500
Please go wait over there.

449
00:41:33,800 --> 00:41:36,500
Noi, take them to wait over there first.

450
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:37,500
Yes, please.

451
00:41:40,500 --> 00:41:42,500
Who are they, Father?

452
00:41:42,700 --> 00:41:43,300
Well …

453
00:41:43,500 --> 00:41:47,500
I see that you look for jobs seriously.

454
00:41:48,200 --> 00:41:49,500
I am not at ease as well.

455
00:41:50,500 --> 00:41:51,500
I want to make money too.

456
00:41:52,500 --> 00:41:55,500
Now, luck is on our side.

457
00:41:56,200 --> 00:42:00,500
These people told me that the Japanese soldiers are selling out the oil .

458
00:42:01,500 --> 00:42:03,500
They will sell it to us cheaply.

459
00:42:03,800 --> 00:42:06,500
After receiving the oil, we'll sell it further.

460
00:42:07,000 --> 00:42:09,500
It will be very profitable.

461
00:42:11,500 --> 00:42:14,500
Did they secretly stole the oil from the Japanese?

462
00:42:14,900 --> 00:42:17,500
Hey, even they stole it,

463
00:42:18,100 --> 00:42:19,500
we know how much the Japanese soldiers

464
00:42:19,800 --> 00:42:22,500
are taking advantage of our country,

465
00:42:23,500 --> 00:42:24,500
so they deserve it.

466
00:42:26,500 --> 00:42:29,500
If we get the oil, it must sell well.

467
00:42:30,500 --> 00:42:33,500
We will be able become a millionaire like before.

468
00:42:34,100 --> 00:42:36,500
This is the advantage of war.

469
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:38,500
Father.

470
00:42:38,800 --> 00:42:40,500
Don't scold me.

471
00:42:41,500 --> 00:42:42,500
Just this one time.

472
00:42:42,900 --> 00:42:44,500
Later, if you are married to Tian,

473
00:42:44,900 --> 00:42:46,500
we won't suffer anymore.

474
00:42:47,500 --> 00:42:48,500
Okay?

475
00:43:19,500 --> 00:43:20,500
Li

476
00:43:21,500 --> 00:43:23,500
What's the matter.

477
00:43:28,500 --> 00:43:29,500
About Dong…

478
00:43:30,500 --> 00:43:34,500
I let people search for his relatives but they couldn't find them.

479
00:43:35,500 --> 00:43:37,500
The body was taken out of the water.

480
00:43:37,900 --> 00:43:38,500
It shouldn't be stored for a very long time.

481
00:43:39,500 --> 00:43:43,500
I think we should hurry and cremate it.

482
00:43:45,500 --> 00:43:46,500
That's true.

483
00:43:46,900 --> 00:43:49,500
He died unnaturally and in the water.

484
00:43:53,500 --> 00:43:55,500
But I think I think we shouldn't burn it yet.

485
00:43:56,500 --> 00:43:57,500
Why?

486
00:44:01,500 --> 00:44:03,500
When the body was found,

487
00:44:04,500 --> 00:44:05,500
all the workers heard Chan said

488
00:44:07,500 --> 00:44:11,500
that you may be involved in his death.

489
00:44:14,500 --> 00:44:16,500
If we hurry to burn it now,

490
00:44:17,500 --> 00:44:19,500
people will think that we are hiding something.

491
00:44:21,500 --> 00:44:23,500
But the evidence is clear already

492
00:44:24,500 --> 00:44:26,500
that Dong stole the money and ran away.

493
00:44:27,500 --> 00:44:30,500
Don't you believe me and still doubt in me?

494
00:44:33,500 --> 00:44:35,500
I believe in the evidence.

495
00:44:36,500 --> 00:44:37,500
If you didn't do it,

496
00:44:39,500 --> 00:44:40,500
you don't have to worry.

497
00:44:45,500 --> 00:44:46,500
One more thing,

498
00:44:47,500 --> 00:44:49,500
due to Zhang's death last time,

499
00:44:50,500 --> 00:44:52,500
the association members haven't got along well like before.

500
00:44:53,500 --> 00:44:58,500
Maybe someone will take this opportunity to frame you again.

501
00:44:59,500 --> 00:45:01,500
Wait another seven days.

502
00:45:02,500 --> 00:45:05,500
If relatives or someone else doesn't complain about Dong's death,

503
00:45:06,500 --> 00:45:07,500
until that day, we can burn the body.

504
00:45:08,500 --> 00:45:10,500
So that no one can accuse us.

505
00:45:24,500 --> 00:45:26,500
Hurry up and look at Dong's body.

506
00:45:26,700 --> 00:45:28,500
I'm sure there must be something.

507
00:45:29,500 --> 00:45:32,500
Otherwise, Madam Li won't care about his body and hurry for the cremation.

508
00:45:33,500 --> 00:45:34,500
There's probably nothing.

509
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:39,500
because I didn't see any wounds or bruises when he was brought out from the water.

510
00:45:40,000 --> 00:45:41,500
No wounds and no injuries,

511
00:45:41,900 --> 00:45:43,500
but he may not drown normally.

512
00:45:44,500 --> 00:45:47,500
Have you forgotten that Jia is good at concocting pills?

513
00:45:48,500 --> 00:45:50,500
She might use poison to kill Dong and threw him into the water.

514
00:45:51,500 --> 00:45:52,500
Yes, Madam.

515
00:46:38,500 --> 00:46:41,500
Dong, my master ordered me to do.

516
00:46:41,800 --> 00:46:43,500
I didn't insult you at all.

517
00:47:27,500 --> 00:47:31,500
Oh, Mr. Yang. I was so shocked. I thought it was Dong's ghost.

518
00:47:32,500 --> 00:47:34,500
I'm scared.

519
00:47:35,000 --> 00:47:36,500
If it was Dong's ghost, he would have killed you for sure.

520
00:47:37,500 --> 00:47:38,500
Why are you messing with his body?

521
00:47:38,900 --> 00:47:40,500
No, it's Madam Chan.

522
00:47:41,500 --> 00:47:44,500
It's nothing. Madam Chan doesn't know about it.

523
00:47:44,900 --> 00:47:47,500
I came here on my own. I just wanted to pay homage to Dong's body.

524
00:47:48,000 --> 00:47:50,500
Because when he was alive, I often argued with him.

525
00:47:50,600 --> 00:47:51,500
Don't lie.

526
00:47:52,500 --> 00:47:55,500
I saw you sneaking out of the house.

527
00:47:55,800 --> 00:47:56,500
So I followed you here.

528
00:47:57,500 --> 00:47:59,500
What did she tell you to do?

529
00:48:01,500 --> 00:48:02,500
Hmm?

530
00:48:06,500 --> 00:48:07,500
Someone's coming.

531
00:48:22,500 --> 00:48:23,500
Are you really going to sleep here?

532
00:48:24,500 --> 00:48:25,500
You don't have to watch over him actually.

533
00:48:26,000 --> 00:48:27,500
There's nothing valuable in the coffin.

534
00:48:28,500 --> 00:48:29,500
No one would steal it.

535
00:48:29,900 --> 00:48:31,500
It's an order of my boss.

536
00:48:32,500 --> 00:48:35,500
Up to you, I'll go get you a pillow and a mat.

537
00:48:43,500 --> 00:48:46,500
Madam let Aunt Jia sleep here and watch over Dong's body herself?

538
00:48:58,500 --> 00:48:59,500
You ca go now.

539
00:49:30,500 --> 00:49:33,500
If someone sees Dong's body in this condition, we'll be in trouble.

540
00:49:44,500 --> 00:49:45,500
What?

541
00:49:46,500 --> 00:49:48,500
Did Madam Li let Jia sleep there and watch over the body?

542
00:49:48,600 --> 00:49:49,300
Yes, Madam.

543
00:49:49,500 --> 00:49:53,500
It means we're on the right direction. There must be something with the body.

544
00:49:53,900 --> 00:49:56,500
Actually I almost got the information

545
00:49:57,000 --> 00:49:58,500
if Mr. Yang didn't interfere it.

546
00:49:59,200 --> 00:50:02,500
Now it's hard to go back or find evidence from the body.

547
00:50:04,500 --> 00:50:07,500
What's wrong with my son?

548
00:50:07,800 --> 00:50:09,500
He's always in my way all the time?

549
00:50:10,000 --> 00:50:13,500
I understand that he loves and wants to protect his brother.

550
00:50:14,500 --> 00:50:17,500
But I don't get it why he intervenes and helps conceal the murderer.

551
00:50:18,100 --> 00:50:20,500
It's because this has something to do with Mr. Tian.

552
00:50:21,500 --> 00:50:22,500
If Madam Li and Jia really did this,

553
00:50:23,500 --> 00:50:25,500
the person who would be in trouble is Mr. Tian.

554
00:50:26,100 --> 00:50:27,500
So Mr. Yang wants to help them.

555
00:50:31,500 --> 00:50:33,500
So what are we going to do next?

556
00:50:36,500 --> 00:50:38,500
Since we can't handle this by ourselves,

557
00:50:39,500 --> 00:50:41,500
we have to lend other's hands to help us.

558
00:50:51,500 --> 00:50:52,500
Are you really going to sleep here?

559
00:50:53,500 --> 00:50:54,500
You don't have to watch over him actually.

560
00:50:55,500 --> 00:50:57,500
There's nothing valuable in the coffin.

561
00:50:58,000 --> 00:50:59,500
No one would steal it.

562
00:51:00,500 --> 00:51:01,500
It's an order of my boss.

563
00:51:11,500 --> 00:51:13,500
Why did Aunt Jia have to guard Dong's body?

564
00:51:14,500 --> 00:51:15,500
What is she afraid of?

565
00:51:21,500 --> 00:51:22,500
Lady Pin.

566
00:51:25,500 --> 00:51:26,500
Lady Pin.

567
00:51:28,500 --> 00:51:31,500
Are you here to see Tian? He's not here.

568
00:51:31,800 --> 00:51:32,500
He's gone to the warehouse.

569
00:51:33,500 --> 00:51:35,500
No. I'd like to see Aunt Li.

570
00:51:35,800 --> 00:51:37,500
Madam Li is not here. She went out with Aunt Jia.

571
00:51:39,500 --> 00:51:40,500
What about Mr. Song?

572
00:51:41,500 --> 00:51:42,500
Father is not here too.

573
00:51:44,500 --> 00:51:45,500
Lady.

574
00:51:46,500 --> 00:51:47,500
Do you have any business?

575
00:51:49,500 --> 00:51:52,500
Too bad, I'd like to ask them to help stop my father.

576
00:51:53,500 --> 00:51:55,500
What did your father do?

577
00:52:06,500 --> 00:52:07,500
No, sir.

578
00:52:09,500 --> 00:52:10,500
No, please.

579
00:52:11,500 --> 00:52:13,500
Lady Pin orders me to stop you from buying it.

580
00:52:14,500 --> 00:52:15,500
Nangnoi.

581
00:52:16,100 --> 00:52:18,500
Will you believe my daughter or me?

582
00:52:18,800 --> 00:52:19,500
I believe Lady Pin.

583
00:52:20,000 --> 00:52:21,500
But I don't believe you and I will buy it.

584
00:52:24,500 --> 00:52:25,500
Stop right now.

585
00:53:00,500 --> 00:53:03,500
Who is this Japanese soldier?

586
00:53:04,000 --> 00:53:06,500
We …

587
00:53:07,500 --> 00:53:10,500
We have been informed that someone had stolen the oil for sale.

588
00:53:12,500 --> 00:53:15,500
Sir, don't harm my father.

589
00:53:16,100 --> 00:53:18,500
He was deceived. We didn't mean to do so. I'm really sorry, sir.

590
00:53:20,500 --> 00:53:21,500
Father.

591
00:53:22,500 --> 00:53:23,500
Quiet!

592
00:53:26,500 --> 00:53:31,500
The offender must be punished.

593
00:53:32,500 --> 00:53:33,500
He must be strapped to the board

594
00:53:34,500 --> 00:53:36,500
and received waterboarding.

595
00:53:37,500 --> 00:53:38,500
You have misunderstood.

596
00:53:39,500 --> 00:53:41,500
We didn't steal your oil.

597
00:53:41,800 --> 00:53:44,500
If you don't believe me, come and see here.

598
00:53:52,500 --> 00:53:55,500
There is only one tank of oil bought from a gas station. Other twos are plain water.

599
00:53:56,000 --> 00:53:58,500
Right! Only one tank of oil.

600
00:53:58,600 --> 00:53:59,500
Yes.

601
00:54:00,300 --> 00:54:01,500
What? What do you mean?

602
00:54:01,800 --> 00:54:03,500
Are you guys deceiving me?

603
00:54:05,500 --> 00:54:06,500
Father, Father.

604
00:54:25,500 --> 00:54:29,500
Sir, don't punish Father. He was fooled.

605
00:54:30,500 --> 00:54:33,500
Yes, I really don't know.

606
00:54:34,200 --> 00:54:34,700
But …

607
00:54:35,500 --> 00:54:39,500
If there is one tank of oil and the rest is water,

608
00:54:40,000 --> 00:54:42,500
that means I didn't steal oil. I'm not guilty.

609
00:54:43,500 --> 00:54:45,500
What not guilty?

610
00:54:47,500 --> 00:54:49,500
This is considered cooperation with them.

611
00:54:50,500 --> 00:54:51,500
Impersonate Japanese soldiers

612
00:54:56,500 --> 00:54:59,500
Sir, please don't pour oil into Father's mouth.

613
00:54:59,800 --> 00:55:00,500
Please.

614
00:55:00,600 --> 00:55:01,500
No.

615
00:55:03,500 --> 00:55:04,500
Fine.

616
00:55:06,500 --> 00:55:11,500
For the sake of your daughter's gratitude,

617
00:55:12,500 --> 00:55:13,500
I will not press charges.

618
00:55:14,500 --> 00:55:17,500
But don't do this again in the future.

619
00:55:18,500 --> 00:55:20,500
Be obedient to your daughter.

620
00:55:21,500 --> 00:55:22,500
Do you understand?

621
00:55:23,500 --> 00:55:28,500
Yes, I will listen to my daughter from now on.

622
00:55:37,500 --> 00:55:38,500
Good.

623
00:55:45,500 --> 00:55:46,500
Enjoy your meal, Mr. Yang.

624
00:55:47,500 --> 00:55:48,500
I'll buy this meal for you.

625
00:55:49,500 --> 00:55:52,500
It's alright, you don't have much money now, right?

626
00:55:53,500 --> 00:55:55,500
I'm still okay for this. You helped me today.

627
00:55:56,000 --> 00:55:58,500
Otherwise, my father would probably got scammed and lost more money.

628
00:56:02,500 --> 00:56:06,500
Then I think the noodles are too cheap.

629
00:56:07,500 --> 00:56:12,500
For a Japanese soldier like me, I'd rather eat something more expensive.

630
00:56:16,500 --> 00:56:21,500
If I report the Japanese soldiers that someone was impersonating them,

631
00:56:21,500 --> 00:56:23,500
how do you think he will be punished?

632
00:56:25,500 --> 00:56:27,500
So the noodles are fine for me.

633
00:56:27,500 --> 00:56:28,500
Let's eat.

634
00:56:57,500 --> 00:56:58,500
Boy.

635
00:57:00,500 --> 00:57:01,100
Sorry.

636
00:57:01,200 --> 00:57:01,700
I'm sorry.

637
00:57:04,500 --> 00:57:05,500
Thanks.

638
00:57:08,500 --> 00:57:09,500
I'm so sorry.

639
00:57:16,500 --> 00:57:17,500
Let's go.

640
00:57:19,500 --> 00:57:21,500
Thank you for today.

641
00:57:23,500 --> 00:57:25,500
But no matter what,

642
00:57:26,500 --> 00:57:29,500
the only way I can save my palace is to marry Tian.

643
00:57:32,500 --> 00:57:33,500
Lady Pin.

644
00:57:34,500 --> 00:57:36,500
Tian definitely doesn't love you.

645
00:57:37,500 --> 00:57:38,500
Do you really love him?

646
00:57:40,500 --> 00:57:42,500
Tian is handsome, polite and kind.

647
00:57:43,500 --> 00:57:44,500
Whoever gets married to him will be happy.

648
00:57:46,500 --> 00:57:47,500
I didn't ask if you are getting married.

649
00:57:48,500 --> 00:57:49,500
I asked if you love him.

650
00:57:53,500 --> 00:57:55,500
It doesn't change a thing.

651
00:57:56,500 --> 00:57:59,500
I will have to marry Tian for my palace's survival.

652
00:58:01,500 --> 00:58:04,500
Anyway, thanks again for today.

653
00:58:05,500 --> 00:58:06,500
I got to go back.

654
00:58:07,500 --> 00:58:08,500
Don’t accompany me.

655
00:59:12,500 --> 00:59:14,500
It's getting worse each day.

656
00:59:15,500 --> 00:59:18,500
I don't know who else to ask for help to sort this out.

657
00:59:19,500 --> 00:59:21,500
I think of you

658
00:59:22,500 --> 00:59:24,500
as the only one I can count on.

659
00:59:26,500 --> 00:59:32,500
Do you think Li has something to do with the death of a worker?

660
00:59:33,500 --> 00:59:35,500
And what about Big Brother?

661
00:59:37,500 --> 00:59:39,500
He doesn't say anything.

662
00:59:41,500 --> 00:59:47,500
Honestly, I still couldn't find any evidence that could clearly sue Madam Li.

663
00:59:50,500 --> 00:59:52,500
If this leaks out,

664
00:59:53,500 --> 00:59:55,500
The Five Dragons Association will definitely be damaged.

665
00:59:59,500 --> 01:00:00,500
But are you sure

666
01:00:01,500 --> 01:00:03,500
that you really came here for this reason?

667
01:00:05,500 --> 01:00:10,500
Not because you want to borrow my hands to get rid of Li and Tian

668
01:00:11,000 --> 01:00:15,500
to let your son Yang to take the position of Big Brother?

669
01:00:15,800 --> 01:00:16,500
Right?

670
01:00:29,500 --> 01:00:30,500
I am joking.

671
01:00:31,500 --> 01:00:33,500
Everyone knows how much you loves

672
01:00:34,500 --> 01:00:39,500
and are loyal to the Song Family and our Five Dragons Association.

673
01:00:44,500 --> 01:00:45,500
Yes, sir.

674
01:00:47,500 --> 01:00:51,500
I have brought you the news. How you'll handle it

675
01:00:52,500 --> 01:00:54,500
is up to you.

676
01:00:55,500 --> 01:00:56,500
And I was sure that

677
01:00:57,500 --> 01:01:04,500
no matter what you do, you are also loyal to the association just like me.

678
01:01:05,200 --> 01:01:07,500
It's definitely not for your own benefit.

679
01:01:15,500 --> 01:01:18,500
Do you think Mr. Ma will help us?

680
01:01:19,500 --> 01:01:23,500
If he really help us, the Song family's reputation would be damaged.

681
01:01:24,300 --> 01:01:25,500
Will Mr. Song be in trouble?

682
01:01:26,500 --> 01:01:29,500
He's a talented man. He can handle this matter.

683
01:01:29,800 --> 01:01:33,500
Besides, now we need to find a way to get Madam Li and Tian as quickly as possible.

684
01:01:34,200 --> 01:01:35,500
Are you sure it's worth it?

685
01:01:35,900 --> 01:01:38,500
If we get caught, the two of us will be in real trouble.

686
01:01:39,000 --> 01:01:42,500
Doing this is like bringing enemies to our home.

687
01:01:42,800 --> 01:01:43,500
So is there any other way?

688
01:01:44,500 --> 01:01:46,500
Besides, I've already said it.

689
01:01:46,800 --> 01:01:48,500
We can't fix anything now.

690
01:01:50,500 --> 01:01:52,500
A man like Mr. Ma,

691
01:01:52,500 --> 01:01:55,500
he won't let this matter go silent without doing anything absolutely.

692
01:01:57,500 --> 01:01:58,500
I'm really curious

693
01:01:59,500 --> 01:02:04,500
what method Mr. Ma will use to deal with Madam Li and Dong's body.

694
01:02:05,500 --> 01:02:07,500
But can we trust Madam Chan?

695
01:02:08,500 --> 01:02:11,500
I'm afraid she will harm us later after we help her.

696
01:02:12,500 --> 01:02:13,500
Because if this plan fails,

697
01:02:14,200 --> 01:02:17,500
Song won't probably be pleased that we mess with this matter.

698
01:02:18,500 --> 01:02:20,500
Just let him be.

699
01:02:21,500 --> 01:02:24,500
He can't even handle the incident in his own home.

700
01:02:25,500 --> 01:02:28,500
How can he be the leader of our association.

701
01:02:30,500 --> 01:02:34,500
Everyone knows about Chan and Li.

702
01:02:35,000 --> 01:02:37,500
They are competing for power to make their own children be the leader.

703
01:02:38,500 --> 01:02:41,500
So why do you help her and side with Chan?

704
01:02:42,500 --> 01:02:43,500
I didn't help her.

705
01:02:44,500 --> 01:02:46,500
I helps people who give me benefits.

706
01:02:47,100 --> 01:02:52,500
If we succeed, Song Family and Big Brother's reputation would be tarnished.

707
01:02:53,200 --> 01:02:55,500
We will use this to destroy his credibility

708
01:02:56,500 --> 01:03:00,500
and remove Big Brother from the head position of the Five Dragons Association.

709
01:03:34,500 --> 01:03:38,500
If you buy it as a gift for girls, they will definitely like it.

710
01:04:02,500 --> 01:04:03,500
Hey.

711
01:04:04,500 --> 01:04:05,500
Don't cry, good boy.

712
01:04:06,500 --> 01:04:08,500
Where is your parents? Hmm?

713
01:04:10,500 --> 01:04:11,500
I'm lost.

714
01:04:23,500 --> 01:04:25,500
No. No. Don't harm me.

715
01:04:26,500 --> 01:04:30,500
Help me, Mei. Help me. Help.

716
01:04:34,500 --> 01:04:35,500
You.

717
01:04:41,500 --> 01:04:42,500
How did you get here?

718
01:05:23,500 --> 01:05:25,500
I thought you've already throw it away.

719
01:05:29,500 --> 01:05:32,500
I think if see you again, I will return it.

720
01:05:33,500 --> 01:05:37,500
But I can't return it now. It's already stained.

721
01:05:38,000 --> 01:05:40,500
It's okay. You keep it.

722
01:05:46,500 --> 01:05:49,500
So are you living here with your two siblings?

723
01:05:50,500 --> 01:05:51,500
Yes.

724
01:05:52,500 --> 01:05:55,500
My parents died when I was a kid.

725
01:05:57,500 --> 01:05:59,500
Have you been raising them since you were a child?

726
01:06:00,500 --> 01:06:02,500
In the past, there was an aunt next door who helped take care of us.

727
01:06:03,500 --> 01:06:05,500
But she moved a long time ago.

728
01:06:07,500 --> 01:06:09,500
You are so good.

729
01:06:12,500 --> 01:06:13,500
I'm not.

730
01:06:14,500 --> 01:06:19,500
If I were really good, my siblings would be happier by now.

731
01:06:20,500 --> 01:06:22,500
You are really good.

732
01:06:23,500 --> 01:06:25,500
Your brother and sister look happy for me.

733
01:06:40,500 --> 01:06:41,500
Come on, let me help.

734
01:06:46,500 --> 01:06:47,500
You got a splinter in your finger.

735
01:06:49,500 --> 01:06:51,500
I'll take it out. It will hurt bit.

736
01:07:01,500 --> 01:07:02,500
Thanks.

737
01:07:26,500 --> 01:07:27,500
Here.

738
01:07:30,500 --> 01:07:33,500
This is a film tape.

739
01:07:34,200 --> 01:07:37,500
What is it? It was left outside, so I picked it up.

740
01:07:39,500 --> 01:07:43,500
It's the film used for showing movie on the screen

741
01:07:44,000 --> 01:07:45,500
to tell stories.

742
01:07:46,500 --> 01:07:48,500
I don't know it. I've never seen it. I want to see it.

743
01:07:50,500 --> 01:07:51,500
Such a pity.

744
01:07:52,500 --> 01:07:56,500
This is a war period. I can't take you two to watch it.

745
01:07:58,500 --> 01:07:59,500
How about this?

746
01:08:00,500 --> 01:08:04,500
I will find a movie for you to watch. I promise.

747
01:08:05,100 --> 01:08:05,600
Really? Promise me.

748
01:08:17,500 --> 01:08:23,500
That day, when Bai Suzhen decided to come down to the human world,

749
01:08:24,500 --> 01:08:26,500
she found love with a handsome young man

750
01:08:28,500 --> 01:08:32,500
and gave birth to a baby named Lin.

751
01:08:33,000 --> 01:08:34,500
However, a priest intervene.

752
01:09:54,500 --> 01:09:55,500
It's dark outside.

753
01:09:57,500 --> 01:09:59,500
Let's go. I'll see you out.

754
01:10:12,500 --> 01:10:14,500
Thank you very much for sending my brother home today.

755
01:10:15,500 --> 01:10:19,500
Actually, I pass this area often

756
01:10:20,000 --> 01:10:21,500
but never been in this this alley.

757
01:10:22,000 --> 01:10:23,500
Otherwise,

758
01:10:24,500 --> 01:10:27,500
The two of us must have known each other sooner.

759
01:10:30,500 --> 01:10:33,500
Alright, it's the main road now.

760
01:10:38,500 --> 01:10:39,500
Some day later,

761
01:10:40,500 --> 01:10:42,500
shall we take the kids out for dessert? I have a favorite shop.

762
01:10:43,500 --> 01:10:44,500
I think the kids will like it.

763
01:10:49,500 --> 01:10:50,500
I don't think so.

764
01:10:52,500 --> 01:10:54,500
Don't come here again.

765
01:10:54,500 --> 01:10:56,500
Why?

766
01:10:58,500 --> 01:11:00,500
My world is like this alley.

767
01:11:01,500 --> 01:11:03,500
You just walk past and then leave.

768
01:11:05,500 --> 01:11:07,500
You shouldn't associate with it.

769
01:11:10,500 --> 01:11:12,500
The two of us just happened to meet.

770
01:11:15,500 --> 01:11:18,500
My world and your world are different worlds.

771
01:11:19,500 --> 01:11:23,500
But for me, we all live in the same world.

772
01:11:24,500 --> 01:11:26,500
Whether you are rich or poor,

773
01:11:27,500 --> 01:11:29,500
we can be friends.

774
01:11:32,500 --> 01:11:35,500
You say this because you don't know my world.

775
01:11:40,500 --> 01:11:41,500
Good luck.

776
01:12:40,500 --> 01:12:43,500
Stop, don't move the body anywhere.

777
01:12:43,800 --> 01:12:44,500
Open it.

778
01:12:47,500 --> 01:12:49,500
What should we do?

779
01:12:50,000 --> 01:12:51,500
Whoever got involved in Dong's death

780
01:12:52,000 --> 01:12:54,500
and if it affects on the Five Dragons Association,

781
01:12:55,000 --> 01:12:56,500
I will punish that person until the very end.

782
01:12:57,500 --> 01:13:01,500
If you are in trouble, come to me. My father can help you.

783
01:13:01,800 --> 01:13:02,500
Who is your father?

784
01:13:03,500 --> 01:13:07,500
These orchids can help us protect Mr. Tian's secret.

785
01:13:08,000 --> 01:13:08,500
Or is Mother with Aunt Jia?
